overview: The fourth of five farewell concerts by the 4 remaining members of the Grateful Dead performed on July 4, 2015 in Chicago, IL. SET 1: Shakedown Street, Liberty, Standing on the Moon, Me and My Uncle, Tennessee Jed, Cumberland Blues, Little Red Rooster, Friend of the Devil, and Deal. SET 2:  Bird Song, The Golden Road (To Unlimited Devotion), Lost Sailor, Saint of Circumstance, West L.A. Fadeaway, Foolish Heart, Drums-Space, Stella Blue, and One More Saturday Night. ENCORE:  U.S. Blues
tagline: What a long strange trip it's been.
title: Grateful Dead: 2015.07.04 - Chicago, IL
